{"tid":1380224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 淘寶真係乜都有得賣","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:23:40.000Z","uid":2646,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2453fc81f484077364aaccf0f7c89e590e8cd06","tid":1380224,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"1. 防毒面具  (裝修必備）<br />\n<br />\n7502防毒半面具 39 rmb~<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.tb.cn/h.eRe0Yd1?sm=a8a278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.tb.cn%2Fh.eRe0Yd1%3Fsm%3Da8a278&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=9c7f4904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.tb.cn/h.eRe0Yd1?sm=a8a278</a><br />\n<br />\n6800防毒全面具 250 rmb~<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.tb.cn/h.eiP8Gv5?sm=d91388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.tb.cn%2Fh.eiP8Gv5%3Fsm%3Dd91388&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=9c57e49b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.tb.cn/h.eiP8Gv5?sm=d91388</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 雷射電筒 (千奇唔好買，幾百/幾千支射出去都好危險嫁！）<br />\n<br />\n200mW 純藍光 85 rmb<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.tb.cn/h.eReYYzp?sm=2db9b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.tb.cn%2Fh.eReYYzp%3Fsm%3D2db9b8&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=33764dc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.tb.cn/h.eReYYzp?sm=2db9b8</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 煙餅 (2015年有人比人拉過，千奇唔好買有機會犯法）<br />\n發夢個陣見到d狗衝上黎，我掉左幾十粒落地就冇再衝上黎，另外太大煙d狗見唔到我地做緊乜就唔係太好啦<br />\n<br />\n15蚊10粒<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.tb.cn/h.eiPmCNN?sm=f1726f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.tb.cn%2Fh.eiPmCNN%3Fsm%3Df1726f&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=39b67bab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.tb.cn/h.eiPmCNN?sm=f1726f</a><br />\n<br />\n4.電筒（去露營必備）<br />\n<br />\n今次介紹可以係香港買到比較貴既電筒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.price.com.hk/product.php?p=361307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fproduct.php%3Fp%3D361307&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=4c25cec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.price.com.hk/product.php?p=361307</a><br />\n1000流明，310米射程，24000cd，有爆閃功能趕走野狗<br />\n留意返唔包電池要另外買18650 8A電池大約150蚊一粒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.price.com.hk/product.php?p=361252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fproduct.php%3Fp%3D361252&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a0d6d030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.price.com.hk/product.php?p=361252</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家分享有咩千奇唔好買既野"},{"pid":"552e473ed8572927bc3bffec9d74f99f542b9e62","tid":1380224,"uid":208452,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:19:48.000Z","msg":"而家上面仲比運落黎?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ece68ab05df5bc95c334f1fbe54a6ed13a79057b","tid":1380224,"uid":2646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"要自己搵集運<br />\n可以運到落黎"},{"pid":"d70b17f1b10b0b91d0582dceca15ca04f1337401","tid":1380224,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef81fe16e81b23b932acf96ac737dc7dab77020","tid":1380224,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"b38a6b0b58dc80c1931e1b7069213ac0df2706ad","tid":1380224,"uid":2646,"